# index.word — the genesis book's reading order. The boot reads this file first; each line is one
# word I take up, in dependency order (the foundation flats descend from word.word; the rest follow).
# THE ONE declaration of the order: a word is in the store iff it is in this book (the drift gate
# holds the two equal). `I read <word>.` takes up an op/concept word; `I read the able <name>.`
# takes up an able-spec (the able namespace — words/ables/).

